{"tid":227610,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple再曝新專利　Wi-Fi可以給iPhone充電","createTime":"2017-05-03T10:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T14:23:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c0ad3537f55a851decfb813d9fa78b77a79d8b","tid":227610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170502/photo/bkn-20170502213918249-0502_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170502221320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170502213918249-0502_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170502221320&h=9b51396a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple Insider報道，來自美國專利和商標局公開一項專利，蘋果公司（Apple Inc.)在尋找利用無線路由器為iPhone以及其他移動設備進行無線充電的方法，技術工作原理類似於Apple Watch感應充電技術，增加了充電的有效距離。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，蘋果這項新專利名「無線充電和擁有雙頻天線的通訊系統」。從理論上來看，無線電源傳輸是可以發生在700MHz至2700MHz之間的通訊信號、2.4GHz和5.0GHz這兩個頻段中的。<br />\n<br />\n採用類似提高路由器信號質量的波束控制技術，設備發出的信號將可以實現無線充電的電源。蘋果的專利還涉及延長感應充電距離的方法，確提到了雙模電路、雙極化、雙頻貼片天線、替代天線陣列和無線電路配置等技術概念。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這個專利是2015年所提交的。最後，蘋果新一代iPhone確定將會採用某種方式的無線充電，目前還未確定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170502/bkn-20170502213918249-0502_00842_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170502%2Fbkn-20170502213918249-0502_00842_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=fc5a1dea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170502/bkn-20170502213918249-0502_00842_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"30828f6143bbef4e02d2a227cc34bc6d31f1a4b1","tid":227610,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:22:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e75a2a12e44ea0803f072ceaf4cec49e33f00aa1","tid":227610,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎哂專利又唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專利果啲係鬥快拎左先<br />\n個效率可以低到痴線"},{"pid":"6fa508eb88d3ded3c6d5432d87349d2aeda054c0","tid":227610,"uid":20664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎哂專利又唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專利果啲係鬥快拎左先<br />\n個效率可以低到痴線</blockquote><br />\n成個人熟左都未差到1%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eba52386c313ff5862851decee52a98304ffb59","tid":227610,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55ebca408370ab518e444faab21b70cb7ffbf717","tid":227610,"uid":113227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪wifi連去充電底座咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁會好啲 唔係嘅話唔比用線差就麻煩嘢"}]}